Package nz.co.jedsimson.lgp.core.evolution.training

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    TrainingUpdateMessage
    A message sent from a class Trainer to a subscriber (by calling TrainingJob.subscribeToUpdates.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DistributedTrainer<TProgram,TOutput extends Output<TProgram>>
    Trains the model for a given number of runs, in a parallel manner.
    DistributedTrainingJob<TProgram,TOutput extends Output<TProgram>>
    Represents an asynchronous distributed training operation.
    SequentialTrainer<TProgram,TOutput extends Output<TProgram>>
    Trains the model for a given number of runs, in a sequential manner.
    SequentialTrainingJob<TProgram,TOutput extends Output<TProgram>>
    Represents an asynchronous sequential training operation.
    Trainer<TProgram,TOutput extends Output<TProgram>,TMessage extends TrainingUpdateMessage>
    A service capable of training evolutionary models in a particular environment.
    TrainingJob<TProgram,TOutput extends Output<TProgram>,TMessage extends TrainingUpdateMessage>
    Represents an asynchronous training operation.
    TrainingMessages
    Contains the different messages that can be sent from a class Trainer when training asynchronously.
    TrainingResult<TProgram,TOutput extends Output<TProgram>>
    Represents the result of training a model using a runner.
